Fig. 175
); sides and venter greyish yellow. Book-lung covers grayish yellow. Spinnerets brownish. All legs: coxae and trochanters yellow, Fm, Pt and Tb brownish, Mt and Tr yellowish brown. Palps brownish. Palpal structure as in 
